x4freetext: NUCLEI WITH NUCLEON NUMBERS BETWEEN A=79 AND A=96*.-
FRM IS AN OPEN POOL REACTOR WITH A THERMAL
CRYSTALLINE POWDERS OF THE CHEMICAL COMPOUNDS NA-BR,
-ISOTOPICAL COMPOSITIONS AND DENSITIES OF THE SAMPLES
-LIQUID BR(2),CO-BR(3),AND POWDERS OF K-BR AND NA-BR
-DETAILS OF THE SAMPLES ARE GIVEN IN TABLE 4
.POWDERS WERE CAREFULLY DRIED AND HANDLED UNDER
SOLID SUBSTANCES WITH A LIQUID. THE SCATTERING
LENGTH OF THE SOLID IS DETERMINED BY MEASURING
THE RATE OF THE SMALL ANGLE SCATTERING OF SLOW
NEUTRONS AS FUNCTION OF THE KNOWN SCATTERING
.SPIN STATE SCATTERING LENGTHS WERE DERIVED FROM
SUBENT 017 CHANGED TO ZR-96. PRINTING ERROR
.THE AUTHORS POINT OUT,THAT THERE ARE PRACTICALLY
NO SYSTEMATICALLY ERRORS DUE TO THE USED TECHNIQUE
.A SOURCE OF UNCERTAINTY IS CAUSED BY THE CONDITION
OF THE POWDERED SAMPLES, WHICH MAY CONTAIN ABSORBED
AND ADSORBED WATER AND GASES AND DECOMPOSITION
TO AVOID THESE UNCERTAINTIES MEASUREMENTS WERE
PERFORMED ON DIFFERENT COMPOUNDS PARTLY BEFORE AND
